It looks like we might be able to slow down the speed of the live validation, which could be a workaround, then also we face the issue of it being too slow to validate. Anyhow, the trick seems to be:

/* 100 seconds until verifying the field to be validated */
$(document).foundation({abide: { timeout: 100000, patterns: { xxx: /^...$/ } }});
